  <scopecontent id="aspace_37165854608352202f5914a67c4f91ab">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Documents related to various events in Unites States history. Includes items related to the Revolutionary War and the War of 1812, a Washington, D.C. lottery ticket, and prescriptions for alcohol written during Prohibition.</p>  </scopecontent>
